headline: Cummins Announces Appointment of John Gaidoo as Vice President and Chief Legal Officer
summary: COLUMBUS, Ind., April 09, 2025--Cummins Inc. (NYSE: CMI) announced today that John Gaidoo has been appointed as Vice President and Chief Legal Officer, effective June 1. He will succeed Nicole Lamb-Hale following her transition to Chief Administrative Officer and Corporate Secretary.
